title: Melbourne University Food Co-op
description: Not-for-profit cooperatively-run vegetarian cafe and co-op on the first floor of Union House. Serves hot lunch plates, organic vegan pies, rolls, cakes and sweets, and herbal teas. The co-op sells bulk foods including nutritional yeast, teas, herbs, spices, grains, flour, dried fruit, coconut butter and a couple of non-vegan chocolates. Local, organic mixed fruit, vegetable boxes can be ordered weekly for pick up.
streetAddress: Union Building Level 1, University of Melbourne
